<p>pycryptoのバージョンを変更すればよい</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>pip uninstall pycrypto
</span><span class='line'>pip install PyCrypto==2.3</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>テスト</h3>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>fabric_test.py</span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
